contents.text: The Team Behind Trackers Jeep Safari
We are what we repeatedly do. Excellence then is not an act but a habit.
Our professional staff are dedicated, warm, caring, attentive and knowledgeable with a proven track record in exceptional customer service.
All our drivers are local, expert drivers with years of experience, fully compliant, professionally licensed and with an extensive knowledge of the Island, its history, culture and people.
English speaking individuals with great communication skills, with a friendly, witty nature.
Additionally, our organisation is fortunate enough to employ a number of our guides and drivers whom are bilingual in various languages.
